程序包 xyz.fsgik.common.io

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    FsFile
    Interface to operate file, thread-safe.
    FsFileCache
    File cache service, provides cached IO methods.
    FsFileCache.CacheReadListener
    Listener for cache read.
    FsFileCache.CacheWriteListener
    Listener for cache write.
    FsFileCache.ChunkCache
    Cache interface used for FsFileCache, must support remove listener.
    FsFileCache.ChunkCacheGenerator
    Generator for file chunk cache.
    FsFileCache.ChunkCacheGenerator.RemoveListener
    Chunk cache remove listener.
    FsFileCache.FileAccessGenerator
    Generator for un-cached underlying file access.
    FsFileCache.FileReadListener
    Listener for underlying file read.
    FsFileCache.FileWriteListener
    Listener for underlying file write.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    FsBuffer
    Utilities for Buffer, etc.
    FsFileCache.Builder
    Builder for FsFileCache.
    FsFileCache.Chunk
    Value for chunk cache, holds file chunk data and tail flag.
    FsFileCache.ChunkIndex
    Key for chunk cache, holds file path and index of cached chunk data.
    FsIO
    Input/Output utilities.
  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    FsIOException
    Exception for IO.
